  <brief_title>Comparison of Gait Parameters Between Floor and Sponge Surfaces and Special Shoes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Gait Parameters Between Floor and Sponge Surfaces and Special Shoes in Individuals With Difficulties in Weight-bearing</official_title>
